              <h3 class="sl-step__title">See what worked</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="sl-step__desc">Not "stream more consistently." The AI tells you what broke this stream, what worked, and what your next challenge is.</p>
            <ul class="sl-step__bullets">
              <li>Specific to your numbers, not generic tips</li>
              <li>What went well, what to fix</li>
              <li>Next challenge unlocks automatically</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </button>

        <button class="sl-step" data-screen="3">
