            </div>
            <p class="sl-step__desc">See where you started, where you are, and what's ahead. Levels, streaks, XP — your whole arc in one place.</p>
            <ul class="sl-step__bullets">
              <li>Levels from "Streaming into the void" to "You made it"</li>
              <li>Weekly streak keeps you consistent</li>
              <li>Watch yourself grow over months</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </button>

        <p class="sl-steps-hint">Tap each step to see it in the app</p>
